Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:03.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\blur3\fad(0,0)\i1\move(300,1065,45,1065)}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:06.16,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}哼哼喘着粗气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:10.25,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}沿着走廊一阵风跑来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:14.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}今晚是你最喜欢吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:17.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}你想吃的就是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:18.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\blur3\fad(0,0)\i1}就是这个没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:22.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}加上你就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:27.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}美食和大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:31.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}我是个围裙男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:35.69,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}围裙男孩 在厨房放连招
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:39.16,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}我是个围裙男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:43.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,0)}围裙男孩 你的笑容是绝品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:45.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}我们家团团圆圆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:46.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}笑声满满
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:47.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}客厅活像乐园
